Subject: [PATCH 05/14] Add and document max reasoning effort

Make max a distinct canonical reasoning-effort level above xhigh. Work around the pinned async-openai type at the JSON request/response seams, gate true max by model capability, preserve compatible max-to-xhigh fallback behavior, and document the resulting model and CLI semantics.
